---
title: Veggie Curry with Toasted Cashews & Brown Rice
description: We’ve tried our fair share of curry recipes in the HelloFresh development kitchen, but this stand-out veggie showstopper left us reaching for seconds... and thirds. Packed with vibrant vegetables, topped with fresh coriander and crunchy toasted cashews, and served on a bed of brown rice, it’s hard to decide which part we love most about it. For a curry that will nourish you from the inside out, this recipe is a no-brainer.
